[
  {
    "text": "As time goes on, ",
    "start": "1291",
    "end": "3291"
  },
  {
    "text": "technology improves,",
    "start": "3291",
    "end": "5375"
  },
  {
    "text": "developed countries with",
    "start": "5375",
    "end": "6833"
  },
  {
    "text": "reliable internet access grow faster. ",
    "start": "6833",
    "end": "8958"
  },
  {
    "text": "But for many, many",
    "start": "9583",
    "end": "10916"
  },
  {
    "text": "rural communities",
    "start": "10916",
    "end": "12416"
  },
  {
    "text": "things like basic internet are ",
    "start": "12416",
    "end": "14416"
  },
  {
    "text": "actually very, very difficult ",
    "start": "14416",
    "end": "16083"
  },
  {
    "text": "to come by. ",
    "start": "16083",
    "end": "17416"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, our mission is to ",
    "start": "17416",
    "end": "19500"
  },
  {
    "text": "reduce the digital divide",
    "start": "19500",
    "end": "22041"
  },
  {
    "text": "because it's a matter of opportunity. ",
    "start": "22041",
    "end": "25833"
  },
  {
    "text": "And using AWS technology, \nwe managed to do this. ",
    "start": "25833",
    "end": "29291"
  },
  {
    "text": "Not by laying out \nterrestrial infrastructure, ",
    "start": "29291",
    "end": "32416"
  },
  {
    "text": "but instead directly through space. ",
    "start": "32416",
    "end": "34916"
  },
  {
    "text": "Kacific is a next generation satellite operator",
    "start": "40583",
    "end": "44125"
  },
  {
    "text": "based in Singapore.",
    "start": "44125",
    "end": "45541"
  },
  {
    "text": "We supply ",
    "start": "45541",
    "end": "46541"
  },
  {
    "text": "high speed broadband internet",
    "start": "46541",
    "end": "48916"
  },
  {
    "text": "via Kacific One, our satellite.",
    "start": "48916",
    "end": "51208"
  },
  {
    "text": "Satellite internet is ",
    "start": "51708",
    "end": "53250"
  },
  {
    "text": "actually very complex.",
    "start": "53250",
    "end": "55083"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are many, many layers",
    "start": "55083",
    "end": "56750"
  },
  {
    "text": "and many, many systems.",
    "start": "56750",
    "end": "58666"
  },
  {
    "text": "The AWS Cloud",
    "start": "58666",
    "end": "60000"
  },
  {
    "text": "allowed us to build our own ",
    "start": "60000",
    "end": "61625"
  },
  {
    "text": "unified system to monitor ",
    "start": "61625",
    "end": "63791"
  },
  {
    "text": "the quality of service,",
    "start": "63791",
    "end": "65333"
  },
  {
    "text": " and we never looked back since. ",
    "start": "65333",
    "end": "67291"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today our service area",
    "start": "67708",
    "end": "69416"
  },
  {
    "text": "covers over 600 million ",
    "start": "69416",
    "end": "71208"
  },
  {
    "text": "people across Asia Pacific.",
    "start": "71208",
    "end": "73125"
  },
  {
    "text": "Most importantly, ",
    "start": "73125",
    "end": "74666"
  },
  {
    "text": " areas that do not",
    "start": "74666",
    "end": "76041"
  },
  {
    "text": " have sufficient connectivity.",
    "start": "76041",
    "end": "78250"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here in Tanay, Rizal,",
    "start": "80541",
    "end": "83125"
  },
  {
    "text": " there is not any ",
    "start": "83583",
    "end": "84958"
  },
  {
    "text": "connectivity to the outside world.  ",
    "start": "84958",
    "end": "87291"
  },
  {
    "text": "The shortest way for them to get it is ",
    "start": "87291",
    "end": "89583"
  },
  {
    "text": "they have to bring the cell phone",
    "start": "89583",
    "end": "90958"
  },
  {
    "text": " to the mountain, at the highest point ",
    "start": "90958",
    "end": "92750"
  },
  {
    "text": "there is a tree they have to climb \nto get good signal. ",
    "start": "92750",
    "end": "95583"
  },
  {
    "text": " But now,",
    "start": "107791",
    "end": "108791"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the satellite",
    "start": "108791",
    "end": "109750"
  },
  {
    "text": "the dish communicates to the satellite",
    "start": "109750",
    "end": "112291"
  },
  {
    "text": "and then it's beamed back to you.",
    "start": "112291",
    "end": "113916"
  },
  {
    "text": "That whole process",
    "start": "113916",
    "end": "115625"
  },
  {
    "text": "just takes a half a second or so.",
    "start": "115625",
    "end": "117375"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you compare it to the cost of cable internet, ",
    "start": "117375",
    "end": "120583"
  },
  {
    "text": "the price of connecting the cable from this village",
    "start": "120583",
    "end": "123708"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the road is probably ",
    "start": "123708",
    "end": "125750"
  },
  {
    "text": "a hundred times what you'll ",
    "start": "125750",
    "end": "127583"
  },
  {
    "text": "spend on a satellite connection.",
    "start": "127583",
    "end": "130207"
  },
  {
    "text": "With the efficiency and scalability of AWS, ",
    "start": "130208",
    "end": "133415"
  },
  {
    "text": "we have reduced the overall work",
    "start": "133416",
    "end": "135458"
  },
  {
    "text": "by as much as 75%.",
    "start": "135458",
    "end": "137958"
  },
  {
    "text": "Therefore, the internet is",
    "start": "137958",
    "end": "139375"
  },
  {
    "text": "a lot more affordable",
    "start": "139375",
    "end": "140583"
  },
  {
    "text": "and a lot more accessible.",
    "start": "140583",
    "end": "142540"
  },
  {
    "text": "How it will affect the future? ",
    "start": "165625",
    "end": "167583"
  },
  {
    "text": "We're hoping that",
    "start": "167583",
    "end": "168790"
  },
  {
    "text": "because of the connectivity,",
    "start": "168791",
    "end": "170291"
  },
  {
    "text": "we’ll have knowledgeable people",
    "start": "170291",
    "end": "171958"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the community, ",
    "start": "171958",
    "end": "173125"
  },
  {
    "text": "then they can ",
    "start": "173125",
    "end": "173708"
  },
  {
    "text": "pioneer their future.",
    "start": "173708",
    "end": "175250"
  },
  {
    "text": "And have the power",
    "start": "175916",
    "end": "177708"
  },
  {
    "text": " to say, no,",
    "start": "178083",
    "end": "179290"
  },
  {
    "text": "we want this place",
    "start": "179291",
    "end": "180708"
  },
  {
    "text": " to be a sanctuary.",
    "start": "180708",
    "end": "182540"
  },
  {
    "text": "I grew up in the Pacific,",
    "start": "183750",
    "end": "185416"
  },
  {
    "text": "in Fiji.",
    "start": "185416",
    "end": "186791"
  },
  {
    "text": "Communication was hard to come by,",
    "start": "186791",
    "end": "189416"
  },
  {
    "text": "so this is really a means ",
    "start": "189416",
    "end": "192958"
  },
  {
    "text": " to give back",
    "start": "192958",
    "end": "193833"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the rural communities",
    "start": "193833",
    "end": "195665"
  },
  {
    "text": "that",
    "start": "195666",
    "end": "196750"
  },
  {
    "text": "I grew up as a part of. ",
    "start": "198291",
    "end": "200583"
  },
  {
    "text": "What connectivity really means",
    "start": "201708",
    "end": "204208"
  },
  {
    "text": "is to be able to connect",
    "start": "204208",
    "end": "205833"
  },
  {
    "text": "to each other. ",
    "start": "205833",
    "end": "207125"
  },
  {
    "text": "Through the partnership of",
    "start": "209291",
    "end": "210333"
  },
  {
    "text": "Kacific and AWS, ",
    "start": "210333",
    "end": "212375"
  },
  {
    "text": "we strive to give ",
    "start": "212791",
    "end": "215041"
  },
  {
    "text": "these young minds",
    "start": "215750",
    "end": "216916"
  },
  {
    "text": "an opportunity to shoot for the stars.",
    "start": "218500",
    "end": "223208"
  }
]